299:void Direct3d11_DynamicVertexBufferData::unlock(int numberOfVertices)
300-{
301-	// Plan 11-09.15 Iter-4 (Test A): CPU-side VB snapshot for radial-pattern
302-	// investigation. Iter-3's per-fan-draw state diagnostic showed 15/16 fan
303-	// samples at byte offset 0 + same shared-ring VB pointer; the math on
304-	// the fan-list IB path is clean (CODEX Bucket A verified) so the next
305-	// question is whether the engine is writing a real quad into CPU memory
