codex
One structural hazard stands out beyond raw ring reuse: `DynamicVertexBufferData::m_offset` is mutable per primitive and overwritten every `prepareToDraw`. I’m verifying the sorter order, because if many primitives prepare before drawing, binding would use the last lock offset, not the submesh’s written slice.
