1014-/**
1015- * Set the sort for a particular phase.
1016- *
1017- * This routine allows the user to control the sort on a phase-by-phase basis.
1018- * Some graphics can be reordered in any manner for best rendering performance,
1019- * while other graphics must be draw back-to-front for correct visuals.  Other
1020- * art should be draw in the order requested (for example, a user interface).
1021- * 
1022- * @param phase The phase for which to set the sort.
1023- * @param sort  The new sort for the phase.
1024- */
